_sText:
An aim map that features much more things to do than in normal aim maps.


Some of them are..

- Much to destroy

- Tunnel to the other side

- Bridge to the other Side

- High brigde

- Hidden Laser AWP

- Bomb place

- Two towers

- Deagles at start, 4 M4's and 4AK's on the high bridge

- 16 Players a site, 32 at all

- And.. a lot of fun! X')


It's not that perfect at all. I know.. But string over that. Nothing's perfect. ;)
But feedback would be still nice.


Greetings,
Z3R0N1C
